In re Resignation of White.

[Cite as In re Resignation of White (1992), 63 Ohio St.3d 1205.]

(No. 92-167 Submitted February 12, 1992 Decided February 19, 1992.)

The resignation of David Otto White as an attorney, Registration No. 0024374, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
